title="Alex Nelson">Alex Nelson</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>The typical proof offered is: consider the lattice of proper ideals of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex> ordered by inclusion. There exists at least one ideal of <fr:tex
